{"tid":962112,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[賀填海華中流感]各位以後有病真係唔需要戴口罩","createTime":"2018-12-30T15:28:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-31T02:32:55.000Z","uid":70786,"like":35,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f17d1d29e1f2a392a03b013627e436dd04cb52f9","tid":962112,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T15:28:17.000Z","msg":"次次我病就戴口罩<br />\nD死廢老賤畜病就唔戴口罩仲要咳同打乞嚏都唔掩口鼻<br />\n搞到我唔病都要戴口罩防班死仆街<br />\n有時防不勝防中招都係因為有D死仆街廢老賤畜<br />\n既然戴口罩都俾D廢老惹病<br />\n咁點解仲要我戴口罩<br />\n<br />\n由今日起我病咗<br />\n我唔會戴口罩之餘<br />\n咳同打乞嚏都要噴落扶手門柄Lift制<br />\n一於玩攬炒睇下邊撚個中流感大鑊D<br />\n<br />\n好似填海華咁<br />\n中流感真係大快人心<br />\n賣港賤畜病住過年啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7907e3c29224618a2ca738c960bcf9b919dad56d","tid":962112,"uid":70786,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T15:35:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.purch.com/w/553/aHR0cDovL3d3dy5saXZlc2NpZW5jZS5jb20vaW1hZ2VzL2kvMDAwLzA0Ny85MTIvb3JpZ2luYWwvc25lZXplLTEwMDMxOS0wMi5qcGc=\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.purch.com%2Fw%2F553%2FaHR0cDovL3d3dy5saXZlc2NpZW5jZS5jb20vaW1hZ2VzL2kvMDAwLzA0Ny85MTIvb3JpZ2luYWwvc25lZXplLTEwMDMxOS0wMi5qcGc%3D&h=20166fb7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家要將D飛沬噴哂落D死廢老身上<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e90483a277d1b0e947d7031d9b118e540ebbbd0f","tid":962112,"uid":106810,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T15:57:13.000Z","msg":"無公德就無公德,唔好美化自己D行為"},{"pid":"a3fd8d59ca1d9692e607dc13d19c4bedd53c5269","tid":962112,"uid":70786,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e90483a277d1b0e947d7031d9b118e540ebbbd0f","tid":962112,"uid":106810,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T15:57:13.000Z","msg":"無公德就無公德,唔好美化自己D行為"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T15:59:57.000Z","msg":"ON9<br />\nD廢老冇公德點解我要有公德<br />\n學佢地咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"073c9d3ffa56bdfcae05